questions.question:
How many times does this loop execute?

for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
    System.out.println(i);
}

What does this loop print?

for (int i = 5; i >= 1; i--) {
    System.out.println(i);
}

What values does this loop print?

for (int i = 0; i <= 10; i += 2) {
    System.out.println(i);
}

What is the final value of sum?

int sum = 0;
for (int i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {
    sum += i;
}

What does this loop count?

int oddCount = 0;
for (int i = 1; i <= 20; i++) {
    if (i % 2 != 0) {
        oddCount++;
    }
}

How many iterations does this loop perform?

for (int count = 0; count < 3; count++) {
    System.out.println(count);
}

What does this string building loop create?

String result = "";
for (int i = 1; i <= 3; i++) {
    result += "*";
}

What range of ages does this loop print?

for (int age = 13; age <= 19; age++) {
    System.out.println(age);
}

How many repetitions does this loop perform?

for (int rep = 1; rep <= 5; rep++) {
    System.out.println("Repetition #" + rep);
}
